title: The Business of Being Yourself, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO11
description: Authenticity is essential for success and happiness.  Whether it's business or life, people are drawn to what's real.  In this episode, Andy Frisella explains the benefits of being yourself and tells you how to become cool with who you are.
